title: Neutron inelastic scattering on iodine and antimony nuclei

x4codes.shortRef: Rept: USSR report to the I.N.D.C., No.106, p.6 (1976)

x4freetext: spectra for scattered neutrons, differential scattering
cross-sections and nuclear temperatures are given.
No Engl.translation as INDC(CCP) rep. at NDS web-site.
Sb -cylinder with radius 22.5 mm and height 45. mm .
I - powder in glass container of 45 mm diameter, 45 mm
Pulse duration 3.0 nsec and flight path 2.0 m.
- without sample at flight path 4 m ,
- at measurement of scattered neutrons on carbon
by long counter made of F3-counter.
Spectrum at energy range 0-300 keV was determined by
neutron attenuation and multiple scattering in sample.
